      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least one physical pump specimen tested under each of the 5 operating conditions with documented fluid preparation.",
      "rationale": "Single FDA generic centrifugal pump specimen tested under all 5 operating conditions. Blood analogue prepared per ASTM F1841 with documented lot traceability. Sample size consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Specimen geometric dimensions verified against nominal CAD within ±0.05 mm."
    },
