    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped out as not required at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied across all 5 operating conditions with experimental agreement within 18%. Solver completed nominally throughout the validation campaign. Informal review of solver robustness identified no issues during the validation runs; the assessment team noted this review was not systematic and did not include fault-injection testing, but judged this acceptable given the commercial solver pedigree and nominal completion of all runs.",
